<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.8">
<l>koṟṟappuḷ ḷoṉṟēṟi maṉṟūṭē varukiṉṟā ṉeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>veṟṟippō rintiraṟku mintiraṉē yokkumā leṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>peṟṟakkā lavaṉākam peṇpiṟantō muyyōmō veṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kaṟṟanūl maṟaiyāḷar kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“He comes into the village square riding a powerful bird,” she declares;</l>
<l>“He is indeed like Indra to even Indra, victorious in battle,” she declares;</l>
<l> “When we, who are born as women, embrace his chest,</l>
<l rend="indent">will we not be saved!” she declares.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram with Vedic experts of learned texts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
